        h2 Lokasi dari File Registry
      section
        h3.bullet %systemroot%\System32\Config
        table(width="600" style="text-align:left").bullet
          tr
            td
              p.bullet - autoexec.nt The file that initializes the MS-DOS environment unless a different startup file is specified in an application's PIF.
              p.bullet - config.nt The file that initializes the MS-DOS environment unless a different startup file is specified in an application's PIF.
              p.bullet - Default The default registry file.
              p.bullet - SAM The SAM (Security Accounts Manager) registry file.
              p.bullet - Security The security registry file.
              p.bullet - Software The application software registry file.
              p.bullet - System The system registry file.
      section
        h3.bullet In a typical Windows XP installation, the %SystemRoot%\System32\Config directory contains these files:
        table(width="600" style="text-align:left").bullet
          tr
            td
              p.bullet AppEvent.evt The application(s) event log file.
              p.bullet DEF$$$$$.del The default registry recovery file.
              p.bullet Default The default registry file.
              p.bullet Default.sav A backup copy of the information contained in the default registry file.
              p.bullet DnsEvent.evt The DNS server event log.
              p.bullet File Rep.evt One of two File Replication Service event log files.
              p.bullet Netlogon.dnb A NetLogon support file.
              p.bullet Netlogon.dns A NetLogon support file.
              p.bullet NTDS.evt The Windows XP directory service event log.
              p.bullet NtFrs.evt The second of two File Replication Service event log files.
      section
        table(width="600" style="text-align:left").bullet
          tr
            td
              p.bullet - SAM The Security Accounts Manager registry file.
              p.bullet - SecEvent.evt The security event log.
              p.bullet - Security The security registry file.
              p.bullet - SOF$$$$$.del The software registry recovery file.
              p.bullet - Software The application software registry file.
              p.bullet - Software.sav A backup copy of the information contained in the software registry file.
              p.bullet - SYS$$$$$.del The system registry recovery file.
              p.bullet - SysEvent.evt The system events log.
              p.bullet - System The system registry file.
              p.bullet - System.alt A copy of the information contained in the system registry file.
              p.bullet - System.sav A backup copy of the information contained in the system registry file.
              p.bullet - Userdiff The file that migrates preexisting user profiles from previous versions of Windows NT to Windows XP.
